cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on aspect-based sentiment analysis using transfer learning with BERT, which is a popular model in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves classification tasks, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of transfer learning and tweaking the tokenizer could be considered as topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
